        "title": "The LIM protein complex establishes a retinal circuitry of visual adaptation by regulating Pax6 \u03b1-enhancer activity", 
        "published": "2017-01-31T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2017-01-31T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 6, 
